1039
01:46:52,212 --> 01:46:53,313
<i>Tidak ada yang selamat.</i>

1040
01:46:53,347 --> 01:46:54,681
Bagaimana denganmu, Pak?

1041
01:46:54,715 --> 01:46:56,650
Kau mau koran <i>Dailygraph?</i>

1042
